For {{ill|Shinkai (divine rank)|lt=Shin’i|ja|神階|1=Shinkai (divine rank)|12=draft|12=draft}}, many shrines achieved the rank of Shōichii over time, particularly with the {{ill|Inari shrines|ja|稲荷神社|12=draft|12=draft}}, which adopted this rank after the main shrine, {{ill|Fushimi Inari Taisha|ja|伏見稲荷大社|12=draft|12=draft}}, received imperial recognition.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://inari.jp/about/history/num04/ |title=稲荷勧請 |publisher=伏見稲荷大社 |accessdate=2024-01-21}}</ref>
