lle/Junior Fifth Rank|qq=}} {{ill|Senior Sixth Rank|ja|正六位|1=Senior Sixth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Sixth Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Sixth Rank|qq=}} {{ill|Junior Sixth Rank|ja|従六位|1=Junior Sixth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Sixth Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Sixth Rank|qq=}} {{ill|Senior Seventh Rank|ja|正七位|1=Senior Seventh Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Seventh Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Seventh Rank|qq=}} {{ill|Junior Seventh Rank|ja|従七位|1=Junior Seventh Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Seventh Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Seventh Rank|qq=}} {{ill|Senior Eighth Rank|ja|正八位|1=Senior Eighth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Eighth Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Eighth Rank|qq=}} {{ill|Junior Eighth Rank|ja|従八位|1=Junior Eighth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Eighth Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Eighth Rank|qq=}} {{ill|Senior Ninth Rank|ja|正九位|1=Senior Ninth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Ninth Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Ninth Rank|qq=}} {{ill|Junior Ninth Rank|ja|従九位|1=Junior Ninth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Ninth Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Ninth Rank|qq=}} {{ill|Senior Initial Rank|ja|大初位|1=Senior Initial Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Initial Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Initial Rank|qq=}} {{ill|Junior Initial Rank|ja|少初位|1=Junior Initial Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Initial Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Initial Rank|qq=}} endRanklist--><!--Senior First Rank--><!--Senior First Rank--><!--Senior First Rank--><!--Senior First Rank--><!--Senior First Rank--><!--Senior First Rank--><!--Senior First Rank--> <!--jawiki derived wikidata interwikis--> [[ko:정1위]] [[zh:正一位]]

{{afc comment|Wikidata entry [[d:Q11123258]] Wikidata name: Senior First Rank [[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 09:11, 11 June 2025 (UTC)}} '''Shōichii''' ({{ill|Senior First Rank|ja|正一位|1=Senior First Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior First Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior First Rank|qq=}}) is one of the highest [[Court Ranks in Japan|Ranks]] in Japan's system of [[:en:Ritsuryō|Ritsuryō]]-based hierarchy and [[Shinkai (divine rank)|Shinkai (divine Ranks)]]. It Ranks above {{ill|Junior First Rank|ja|従一位|1=Junior First Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior First Rank|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior First Rank|qq=}}.<ref>https://www.wakapoetry.net/background/society/court-offices-titles-and-Ranks/court-Ranks/</ref>
== Overview == The Rank of Shōichii has been historically conferred upon individuals who made extraordinary contributions to the state, such as {{ill|Kampaku|ja|関白|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kampaku|qq=|1=kampaku|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1199966}}, [[:en:Daijō-daijin|Daijō Daijin]], or [[:en:Shogun|Shogun]]. However, only seven individuals have ever received this Rank during their lifetime.<ref group="Note">These include {{ill|Fujiwara no Miyako|ja|藤原宮子|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara no Miyako|qq=|1=Fujiwara no Miyako|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11623185}}, [[:en:Fujiwara no Muchimaro|Fujiwara no Muchimaro]], [[:en:Tachibana no Moroe|Tachibana no Moroe]], [[:en:Fujiwara no Nakamaro|Fujiwara no Nakamaro]], [[:en:Fujiwara no Nagate|Fujiwara no Nagate]], {{ill|Minamoto no Katako|ja|源方子|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Katako|qq=|1=Minamoto no Masako|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11564108}}, and [[:en:Sanjō Sanetomi|Sanetomi Sanjō]]. Two of these individuals, Fujiwara no Muchimaro and Sanetomi Sanjō, passed away on the same day they received the Rank.</ref> Most instances of this Rank were posthumously awarded as {{ill|Zoi|lt=Zoi|lt=Zōi|ja|贈位|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zōi|qq=}}.
After [[:en:Meiji Restoration|Meiji Restoration]], the Rank was formalized under the {{ill|Shokuinryō|lt=Shokuinryō|lt=Shokuinrei|ja|職員令|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shokuinrei|qq=}} of 1869.<ref>{{Egov law|215IO0000000325|位階令}}</ref> However, the Rank became symbolic as the role's corresponding duties ceased to exist.
For [[:en:Shinkai (divine rank)|Shin’i]], many shrines achieved the Rank of Shōichii over time, particularly with the [[:en:Inari shrine|Inari shrines]], which adopted this Rank after the main shrine, [[:en:Fushimi Inari-taisha|Fushimi Inari Taisha]], received imperial recognition.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://inari.jp/about/history/num04/ |title=稲荷勧請 |publisher=伏見稲荷大社 |accessdate=2024-01-21}}</ref>
